                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18301209-164-victim1483 t18301209-164-viclabel930"></join>. On the evening of the 27th of November I heard of a loss, and went out; I found the prisoner a hundred yards off with a pig's head, which he said he had picked up in the road - I took him back, and missed a head from the board; it was my father's property.</p>
               <p>
            
