            . I am a Police-officer. I took the prisoner and the head.</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence Two boys ran by me, and threw<xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="183012090086"></xptr>a bundle into a passage of a house in Jerusalem-passage; I took it up, and this gentleman collared me and said it was his - my mother asked the prosecutor if she should bring witnesses, and he said it would be of no use.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18301209-164-person1486">
                  GEORGE 
                  HAMBRIDGE
               <interp inst="t18301209-164-person1486" type="surname" value="HAMBRIDGE"></interp>
