                     <interp inst="t18301209-164-person1486" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . His mother came, said she could bring two or three respectable witnesses, and my father said she was to be sure and bring them; she came to know what it was about - the prisoner was not running, he was walking with two or three more boys, less than himself; it was tied in a handkerchief when I found him.</p>
